{
  "stem": "7744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They also had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because it was a small town, and I think they lived on the outskirts and had sort of a big home with dogs that used to bark.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was told not to go close to them because they were vicious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was, there were a couple of cows and some animals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that was very exciting for a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In fact, I was not too long ago telling my grandchildren that in the attic, there was a huge box of buttons.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And some of them came from military, military wear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I also have a box of buttons which I keep for the kids to play with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I was telling them that I remembered those kind of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember my mother more vividly then I remember the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Of course, I was with her the longest, until the end of war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We spent summers holidaying in different places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In fact, I think I showed you some pictures of that, where I was with my grandparents and my parents in different places.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I can't exactly tell you where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I know one was Zakopane, and there were some, some German resorts that we used to go to in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't really remember going to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, many times I think I must have gone to school, because when the war ended, I did know a little bit how to write.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I must have gone to school, but I don't really remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I can't remember if I had a tutor or if I did go to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I can't remember a class or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
